 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:37:38.000Z","msg":"台灣嘅中華郵政 新台幣存簿儲蓄金融戶口好易開，仲可即時取得簿仔，即場取得郵政VISA debit卡簽帳金融卡，add埋入台灣版LINE Pay, 好方便👍 (不須地址證明）<br />\n<br />\n英國、德國果D banks更可用手機📱足不出戶咁開戶，有埋GBP, EUR VISA or MasterCard debit cards, 隔離posts有講，非常方便。（不須地址證明，有個當地收信地址okay)<br />\n<br />\n瑞士則Dukascopy Bank已可遙距開定個account，取得埋張CHF or USD VISA prepaid card. (用香港地址都okay)<br />\n<br />\n美國則Citibank USA, BoA USA 可當地walk in開戶，一般有USD VISA or MasterCard debit card. 有香港地址證明（如Citibank HK statement)就okay. （或者考慮East West Bank, or <a href=\"http://sablecard.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsablecard.com&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=d33cafaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sablecard.com</a> 遙距開定個account). 美國仲可開埋信用卡，上網search 一些AE 國際轉卡大法以建立你在美國既信用紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲、加拿大既，其他人都有講開，可參考一下。"},{"pid":"85ca73dea619cafb108730087048b78e6d9f194d","tid":2009612,"uid":138226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c41450e686e39c160664c882259db0019a85f3d8","tid":2009612,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ced23a3d2a54ae0d61430c8c63bdb0fd506ab7c","tid":2009612,"uid":138226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebf6f4779f6118f62e927346966914fc29cbe7b5","tid":2009612,"uid":26154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"澳洲係咪間間銀行都唔會寄卡去海外？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T02:42:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:28:35.000Z","msg":"有咩cost"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f60f49d7e3048db78cadaa3ed0dbf62f631fb18","tid":2009612,"uid":138226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a938aa62f156b1b57951ddb1585e8f1ed22e8daf","tid":2009612,"uid":312916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f7b38f9af36ca1ab