itibank statement加 passport可開戶。（YouTube 上也大把教學，<br />\n美國係歡迎大家存入美金在當地）"},{"pid":"ab1e4bace6e24b1619ce424370345bfcd094c351","tid":2009612,"uid":312916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc4ef109cda9135f6422026626a0f43a4cb83c9f","tid":2009612,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"n26唔係有地址就開到啦咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"N26's UK Branch已於2020年4月15日停止英國業務(佢聲稱係因為Brexit而停止英國業務, 但好多評論指係佢地客戶人數不足, 英國只有200,000個N26 UK客戶, 遠較Monzo Bank的4 million及Starlingbank的1 million為少)。<br />\n<br />\n所以只能把英鎊轉番去其他UK's Banks (如果你是N26 Euro Account, 即是Eurozone地址, 則不受影響). <br />\n<br />\nTwitter上唔少英國人對N26's UK Branch既決定好不滿, 但也沒有辦法, 惟有用其他UK's Banks."},{"pid":"53e9b101c2b00c0d66928d2cb090d6c4baee2dd1","tid":2009612,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1e4bace6e24b1619ce424370345bfcd094c351","tid":2009612,"uid":312916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc4ef109cda9135f6422026626a0f43a4cb83c9f","tid":2009612,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"n26唔係有地址就開到啦咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"N26's UK Branch已於2020年4月15日停止英國業務(佢聲稱係因為Brexit而停止英國業務, 但好多評論指係佢地客戶人數不足, 英國只有200,000個N26 UK客戶, 遠較Monzo Bank的4 million及Starlingbank的1 million為少)。<br />\n<br />\n所以只能把英鎊轉番去其他UK's Banks (如果你是N26 Euro Account, 即是Eurozone地址, 則不受影響). <br />\n<br />\nTwitter上唔少英國人對N26's UK Branch既決定好不滿, 但也沒有辦法, 惟有用其他UK's Banks."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:11:55.000Z","msg":"我個時德國開<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b235900026417e67bed5b87a46627225a311cc","tid":2009612,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"美國都開到花旗🙈"},{"pid":"7665aeb43b40b4e7543606f9f3a7e918356d1b6a","tid":2009612,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18c150e505ac77cde8472e0bcc3dcfb2878de574","tid":2009612,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"美國 boa好似好易開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"真，但要有SSN"},{"pid":"2b856ab49af30271a969e85c4af683db24d5fb17","tid":2009612,"uid":312916,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7665aeb43b40b4e7543606f9f3a7e918356d1b6a","tid":2009612,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18c150e505ac77cde8472e0bcc3dcfb2878de574","tid":2009612,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:38:51.000Z","msg":"美國 boa好似好易開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T06:32:20.000Z","msg":"真，但要有SSN"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"應該間間分行處理方法唔同，有些要求有SSN, 有些不用。<br />\n<br />\n如果開唔到BoA，去Citibank USA當地任何分行開戶仲好。有Citibank HK bank account, global transfer ＄去Citibank USA比較方便一些。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到有些人未必有自己姓名既香港水/電/煤單，<br />\n先用香港既手機電話單開Citibank HK bank account, <br />\n<br />\n之後用Citibank HK bank statement 在美國當地開Citibank USA bank checking account, 最簡便。"}]}